// write_lean_cryptol_module on the SHA-512 sigma helpers in
// isolation. This is the recursion-free slice of SHA-512 that
// surfaces the bit-manipulation primitives the larger module
// exercises (rotate-right, shift-right, xor on [64]) without
// pulling in Cryptol's Merkle-Damgard `fix`.
//
// Once Arc 4.4 has a recursion story, see also the deferred
// test_cryptol_module_sha512.saw which exercises the full functor.

write_lean_cryptol_module
  "SHASigma.cry"
  "test_cryptol_module_sha_sigma.module.lean" [] [];
